	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Richmond Va</placeName>&#44; <date>Jany 7<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1857</date></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>5617</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">My Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">The Sunday School requires<lb/> the folly Books</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">1 doz <persName>Peixotto&#39;s</persName> Catechisms</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">1 &#8220;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;<persName>Henry&#39;s</persName> Class Books&#44;</p>
				<p>I should therefore feel obliged by your<lb/> forwarding them to me by Express&#44; &#38;<lb/> am requested to state that should<lb/> you not have 1 doz <persName>Henry&#39;s</persName> Class Books&#44; you<lb/> will be good enough to send whatever less<lb/> you may have on hand.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">My Brother &#38; family desire their<lb/> kind regards to you&#44; &#38; trusting you<lb/> are in the enjoyment of Health&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I remain&#44; my Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Very Truly Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">G<add>&#63;</add> Jacob</persName></p>
				<p>My Brother delivered a Lecture<lb/> before the Lit Society last <date>Sunday</date><lb/> afternoon&#44; to a very large<lb/> auditory and with great<lb/> success&#8212;on &#8220;the Civilization<lb/> of the Ancients&#44;&#8221; showing the<lb/> predominance of the Hebrew Race<lb/> over the there existing nations</p>
		</body>
